  svc_detail_submission_title:{ht:"📨 Soumisyon Dokiman & Peman USCIS",en:"📨 Document Submission & USCIS Payment",fr:"📨 Soumission de Documents & Paiement USCIS"},
  svc_detail_submission_p1:{ht:"Nou soumèt aplikasyon konplè ou yo bay USCIS epi nou jere peman frè USCIS sou non ou. Depi 2026, USCIS pa aksepte chèk pèsonèl ankò — sèlman lòd peman (money order), kat kredi/debi, oswa peman elektwonik.",en:"We submit your completed applications to USCIS and handle USCIS fee payments on your behalf. Since 2026, USCIS no longer accepts personal checks — only money orders, credit/debit cards, or electronic payments.",fr:"Nous soumettons vos demandes complètes à l'USCIS et gérons les paiements de frais USCIS en votre nom. Depuis 2026, l'USCIS n'accepte plus les chèques personnels."},

